{"article_id":"S8BL4NKydl1ATC0s","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON -","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"A federal judge on Friday ordered former Trump campaign chairman Paul Manafort to jail","depth":7},{"id":2,"text":"to await separate trials on money laundering and fraud charges","depth":7},{"id":3,"text":"following allegations","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"that he sought to obstruct the Russia inquiry","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"while he was on house arrest .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Immediately after U.S. District Judge Amy Jackson revoked Manafort 's bail ,","depth":8},{"id":7,"text":"he was led from a packed courtroom by U.S. marshals .","depth":8},{"id":8,"text":"Meanwhile , Manafort ' s wife , Kathleen , left the courthouse ,","depth":8},{"id":9,"text":"forced to walk a gauntlet of photographers to the door of a black SUV .","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"The family made no comment .","depth":6},{"id":11,"text":"If convicted at trial ,","depth":5},{"id":12,"text":"Manafort faces the prospect","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"of spending the rest of his life in custody .","depth":6},{"id":14,"text":"In a lengthy preamble to her ruling , the judge expressed clear frustration with Manafort ' s conduct ,","depth":5},{"id":15,"text":"saying","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that there appeared to be no terms of release","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"that she believed","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"the defendant would follow .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"\" This is not middle school , \"","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"Jackson said at one point .","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"\" I can ' t take his cell phone ....","depth":6},{"id":22,"text":"I have thought long and hard about this .","depth":7},{"id":23,"text":"I don ' t think","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"I can draft a clear enough order \"","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"setting out conditions of Manafort ' s continuing release .","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"Manafort ,","depth":7},{"id":27,"text":"who just two summers ago was celebrating then-candidate Donald Trump 's nomination at the Republican National Convention ,","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"was charged last week along with Russian business associate Konstantin Kilimnik as part of an alleged scheme","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"to tamper with two witnesses in the existing cases against him .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Prosecutors have asserted","depth":7},{"id":31,"text":"that the alleged obstruction effort ,","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"in which Manafort and Kilimnik sought to coach the testimony of the two unidentified witnesses ,","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"required the revocation of Manafort 's bail ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"sending him to jail","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"to await a July trial in Alexandria , Va. , on bank fraud charges and a separate September trial in Washington , D.C. ,","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"where he faces a vast money laundering and fraud conspiracy .","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"Investigators have claimed","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"that the `` repeated '' contacts occurred","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"while Manafort was under house arrest in Virginia , as a condition of his release .","depth":9},{"id":40,"text":"The witnesses worked with Manafort","depth":9},{"id":41,"text":"in organizing a group of former European officials","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"who lobbied within the United States","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"without registering","depth":12},{"id":44,"text":"as required by law .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"The witnesses told investigators","depth":10},{"id":46,"text":"that they `` understood ''","depth":11},{"id":47,"text":"that Manafort was reaching out","depth":12},{"id":48,"text":"to influence the testimony ,","depth":12},{"id":49,"text":"according to court papers .","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":51,"text":"Ex-Trump campaign chair Paul Manafort , Russian associate hit with obstruction charges","depth":6},{"id":52,"text":"More :","depth":6},{"id":53,"text":"Prosecutors :","depth":7},{"id":54,"text":"Paul Manafort tried to coach witnesses in criminal case","depth":7},{"id":55,"text":"Earlier Friday , federal prosecutors","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"representing Russia special counsel Robert Mueller","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"and Manafort ' s attorneys","depth":8},{"id":58,"text":"clashed in court ,","depth":7},{"id":59,"text":"with prosecutors arguing","depth":8},{"id":60,"text":"that the former Trump aide deserved to be jailed","depth":9},{"id":61,"text":"for \" committing a crime while on bail . \"","depth":9},{"id":62,"text":"\" The danger is that Mr. Manafort will continue to commit crimes , \"","depth":8},{"id":63,"text":"prosecutor Greg Andres told the judge .","depth":8},{"id":64,"text":"Manafort attorney Richard Westling said","depth":7},{"id":65,"text":"his client had `` no way","depth":9},{"id":66,"text":"of knowing ''","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"that his contacts involved potential trial witnesses ,","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"and he asked","depth":10},{"id":69,"text":"that Manafort be provided a list of witnesses","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"so that he would know who to avoid .","depth":9},{"id":71,"text":"`` A clear no-contact rule will solve the problem , ''","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"Westling argued .","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"`` This will never happen again . ''","depth":8},{"id":74,"text":"Andres countered","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"that it was `` inconceivable ''","depth":9},{"id":76,"text":"that Manafort would not know","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"who would be witnesses against him .","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"President Trump , meanwhile , sought to distance himself Friday from his former adviser .","depth":6},{"id":79,"text":"\" Manafort has nothing to do with our campaign , \"","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"Trump told reporters","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"gathered at the White House .","depth":9},{"id":82,"text":"\" I feel a little badly about it .","depth":8},{"id":83,"text":"They went back 12 years","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"to get things","depth":10},{"id":85,"text":"that he did 12 years ago ?","depth":10},{"id":86,"text":"But the president declined to say directly","depth":7},{"id":87,"text":"whether he believes","depth":8},{"id":88,"text":"Manafort or others","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"who are part of Mueller ' s probe","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"should be pardoned .","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"\" I don ' t want to talk about that , \"","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"the president said .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"\" I do want to see people treated fairly . \"","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"`` Wow , what a tough sentence for Paul Manafort ,","depth":10},{"id":95,"text":"who has represented Ronald Reagan , Bob Dole and many other top political people and campaigns , ''","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"Trump tweeted .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"`` Didn ' t know","depth":10},{"id":98,"text":"Manafort was the head of the Mob .","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"What about Comey and Crooked Hillary and all of the others ?","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"Very unfair ! ''","depth":10}],"relations":[{"parent":201,"left":0,"right":200,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":200,"left":125,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":125,"left":113,"right":124,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":113,"left":110,"right":112,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":110,"left":105,"right":109,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":105,"left":102,"right":104,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":102,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":104,"left":3,"right":103,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":103,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":109,"left":108,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":108,"left":106,"right":107,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":1